under 20 years of age at the time </div><div class="t m145e x4a h2d y12fe ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the Exodus and those who were born to the Israelites and the mixed multi-</div><div class="t m268 x4a h2d y111e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tude during their travels. These had witnessed God&apos;s miraculous leading </div><div class="t m76e x4a h2d yfd6 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">since childhood. In many cases their </div><div class="t m77a x8f h4a y1bd7 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only </div><div class="t m758 x86 h2d y12af ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">memories were of the wilderness </div><div class="t m555 x4a h2d y1f73 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">march and God&apos;s continuing care. In spite of marked evidence of God&apos;s </div><div class="t mf2f x4a h2d y1fd4 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">providence, both parents and children failed to pass the test when confronted </div><div class="t mb63 x4a h2d y1f64 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with hardship. Their experience contains a lesson for those who find it diffi-</div><div class="t m754 x4a h2d yc87 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cult to trust God when faced with loss or trial. </div><div class="t m136b x64 h2d y150c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The life-giving and life-sustaining properties of water were used to illus-</div><div class="t m5fa x4a h2d y1066 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trate the need of the soul for blessings that come only from God and without </div><div class="t me3d x113 h6c y1e12 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">49 </div><div class="t m1180 x26 h2d y2075 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">?Kb&apos; </div><div class="t m15af x4a h2d y1eac ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">F</div><div class="t m4244 x26 h2d y1eac ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ULM </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
